queries.query: select author from author where id = $1;
queries.name: get_by_id

queries.query:
select author, array_agg(book) as books
from author
join book on author.id = book.author_id
group by author.id;
queries.name: get_all_with_books

queries.query:
select author from author
order by similarity(name, $1);
